```
                     Preamble
```

SlateOS is built on the belief that users should have ownership, control, and freedom over their computing devices.

This software is provided as free and open-source software. Users have the freedom to study how SlateOS works, modify it, improve it, and share their improvements with others.

The SlateOS project believes that operating systems should respect user privacy, transparency, and personal control.

The purpose of this license is to ensure that SlateOS and future improvements remain available to the community.

